description: ~TiddlyWiki Tid2png

<div class="prose max-w-none">

支持导出图片，包括指定 tiddler, 固定区域，甚至直接当作窗口截图工具

!! optional plugins dependencies

* neotw-swal2: preview exported png
* nprogress: progress bar for export png

!! usage

```html
<$tid2png text='use id' customSelector="#export" />
<$tid2png text='use class' customSelector=".export" />
<$tid2png text='use data' customSelector="[data-export]" />

<div id="export" data-export class='export'> export area </div>
```

